  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "integer-partition",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/integer-partition/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "给你一个正整数，比如 4，你能把它拆成几个正整数的和？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "integer-partition",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/integer-partition/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.7,
      "size": 43200,
      "text": "4、3加1、2加2、2加1加1、还有1加1加1加1，一共五种。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "integer-partition",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/integer-partition/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "只要不计较加数的顺序，每一种写法就叫做一个分拆。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "integer-partition",
      "section_id": "count",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "count-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/integer-partition/xiaoxiao/count-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "把 n 的分拆总数记作 p(n)，于是 p(4) 等于 5。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "integer-partition",
      "section_id": "count",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "count-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/integer-partition/xiaoxiao/count-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "p(n) 随 n 增长得飞快，p(10) 就已经是 42。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "integer-partition",
      "section_id": "count",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "count-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/integer-partition/xiaoxiao/count-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "我们用动态规划逐个凑出部件，就能高效算出 p(n)。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "integer-partition",
      "section_id": "young",
      "line_id": "yg-1",
      "filename": "young-yg-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/integer-partition/xiaoxiao/young-yg-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "每个分拆都能画成一张杨氏图：一个部件就是一行方块。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "integer-partition",
      "section_id": "young",
      "line_id": "yg-2",
      "filename": "young-yg-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/integer-partition/xiaoxiao/young-yg-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "部件从大到小自上而下排列，方块左对齐，像一级级台阶。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "integer-partition",
      "section_id": "young",
      "line_id": "yg-3",
      "filename": "young-yg-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/integer-partition/xiaoxiao/young-yg-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "这张图让抽象的和，变成看得见摸得着的形状。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "integer-partition",
      "section_id": "conjugate",
      "line_id": "conj-1",
      "filename": "conjugate-conj-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/integer-partition/xiaoxiao/conjugate-conj-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.04,
      "size": 32688,
      "text": "把杨氏图沿主对角线翻转，行变成列、列变成行。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "integer-partition",
      "section_id": "conjugate",
      "line_id": "conj-2",
      "filename": "conjugate-conj-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/integer-partition/xiaoxiao/conjugate-conj-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 27936,
      "text": "翻转后读到的新分拆，就是原分拆的共轭分拆。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "integer-partition",
      "section_id": "conjugate",
      "line_id": "conj-3",
      "filename": "conjugate-conj-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/integer-partition/xiaoxiao/conjugate-conj-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "再翻一次就回到原样，可见共轭是一种优雅的对称。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "integer-partition",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/integer-partition/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "选一个 n，用上一个下一个逐张翻看它的所有分拆。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "integer-partition",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/integer-partition/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "再点显示共轭，看虚线框如何把图形转置过来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "integer-partition",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
